OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779718268
OL,3,CFarmers reflect on impact of war in
OL,4,Cmiddle east on UK agriculture
OL,6,FFarmers have spent weeks and months
OL,7,Fpreparing for this year's Devon County
OL,8,FShow - a highlight on the calendar
OL,9,Fafter the long winter months, but
OL,10,Fthere's been another big topic of
OL,11,Fconversation amongst them.
OL,13,FAs they admire each other's animals in
OL,14,Fthe show ring, thoughts turn to the
OL,15,Fimpact a war thousands of miles away
OL,16,Fin the Middle East is having on them
OL,17,Fhere in the West Country.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779718268
OL,3,CFarmers reflect on impact of war in
OL,4,Cmiddle east on UK agriculture
OL,6,FThe continued rising cost of fuel,
OL,7,Fvital for the running of their farms,
OL,8,Fis a big concern. As is the spiralling
OL,9,Fcosts of fertiliser. So much so, some
OL,10,Ffarmers are having to make a decision
OL,11,Fon whether they can afford to plant
OL,12,Fcrops this year.
OL,14,FDavid Chugg is the regional board
OL,15,Fchair for the NFU. He says farmers
OL,16,Ftypically plan their next crop at this
OL,17,Ftime of year and he fears with margins
OL,18,Fso thin the cost for some will be too
OL,19,Fhigh.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779718268
OL,3,CFarmers reflect on impact of war in
OL,4,Cmiddle east on UK agriculture
OL,6,FHe said: "There are alot of farmers in
OL,7,Fthe arable sector that are really
OL,8,Fstruggling profit wise.
OL,10,F"The fear is when it comes to June, if
OL,11,Fthe price of fertiliser and fuel is
OL,12,Fnot looking to be in a better place,
OL,13,Fthe crops won't be grown next year and
OL,14,Fthe fields will be left fallow."
OL,16,FWith a third of all nitrogen based
OL,17,Fproducts passing Iran on the strait of
OL,18,FHormuz, prices for fertiliser have
OL,19,Frisen by more than #150 a ton and that
OL,20,Fwill have an impact on other products
OL,21,Ftoo.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779718268
OL,3,CFarmers reflect on impact of war in
OL,4,Cmiddle east on UK agriculture
OL,6,FHarpers Feeds, which has stall at this
OL,7,Fyear's county show, has 3000 customers
OL,8,Facross the south west and says it's
OL,9,Ftrying to absorb the rise in costs,
OL,10,Fknowing the pressure farmers are
OL,11,Ffacing.
OL,13,FGlen Johns, Sales Director at Harpers
OL,14,FFeeds, said "All our freight rates,
OL,15,Fand haulage rates have gone up.
OL,17,F"White diesel derv's gone up, that's
OL,18,Fadded another pound a tonne to our
OL,19,Fcosts bringing the raw materials into
OL,20,Four mill, and delivering it out onto
OL,21,Four farms as well."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779718268
OL,3,CFarmers reflect on impact of war in
OL,4,Cmiddle east on UK agriculture
OL,6,F"So it affects everybody." he added.
OL,8,FAlso attending the show is Mark
OL,9,FWeekes. He's a sheep farmer based near
OL,10,FExeter, and says the war in the Middle
OL,11,FEast is having a big impact on his
OL,12,Fcosts.
OL,14,FHe said "Fertiliser, fuel - red diesel
OL,15,F- that has more than doubled in price
OL,16,Fand it's unsustainable for us."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779718268
OL,3,CFarmers reflect on impact of war in
OL,4,Cmiddle east on UK agriculture
OL,6,FCathy Base, a farmer based near
OL,7,FBigbury, says farmers are at a "cross
OL,8,Froads" with the many issues facing
OL,9,Fthem, and need more clear support and
OL,10,Fguidance from the government.
OL,12,FShe said "We don't know what support
OL,13,Fschemes are going to be released.
OL,14,FWe've got an idea, but we don't know
OL,15,Feasy it's going to be for farmers to
OL,16,Faccess them - that's massive."
OL,18,FThe Government said it was "taking
OL,19,Fdecisive action to support farmers by
OL,20,Fcutting red diesel to its lowest rate
OL,21,Fin over 20 years."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
