PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779718268
OL,3,CFarmers reflect on impact of war in
OL,4,Cmiddle east on UK agriculture
OL,6,FIt added it was "committed to
OL,7,Fprotecting the farming sector from
OL,8,Fglobal pressures including the war in
OL,9,FIran."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
